        </a>

        <a href="https://github.com/arkin0x/cyberspace/blob/master/CYBERSPACE_V2.md" class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 hover:border-cyan-500 rounded-lg p-5 transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-cyan-400 group-hover:text-cyan-300 mb-2">→ Full Specification</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
